@Backend_HostAddress = http://localhost:5018

### оНКСВХРЭ ЯРЮРСЯ БЯЕУ ЪВЕЕЙ
GET {{Backend_HostAddress}}/api/cells
Accept: application/json

### нРЙПШРЭ ЪВЕИЙС ╧2 (оПНБЕПЙЮ КНЦХЙХ)
POST {{Backend_HostAddress}}/api/cells/open/2
Accept: application/json

### оНКСВХРЭ ХМТН Н ГЮЙЮГЕ 1001
GET {{Backend_HostAddress}}/api/order/1001
Accept: application/json

### нОКЮРХРЭ ГЮЙЮГ 1001 Х НРЙПШРЭ ЪВЕИЙС
POST {{Backend_HostAddress}}/api/process-payment?orderId=1001